subSubSection.paragraph:
Character sampling includes the 200 archosauromorph characters from Pritchard et al. (2015) combined with additional archosauromorph characters from previous diapsid datasets (Juul, 1994; Gower and Sennikov, 1996; 1997; 
Dilkes, 1998
; Nesbitt et al., 2009; Nesbitt, 2011, 
Ezcurra et al., 2010
), as well as characters employed here for the first time. Novel characters are described in appendix 4. In total, 247 skeletal characters were scored over the taxa considered (appendix 5). The dataset is available online (http://morphobank.org/927) on MorphoBank (O’Leary and Kaufman, 2012).
